title: Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive is the sultry Emilia Clarke
text:
Updated: 12:01 a.m. Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015 | Posted: 12:01 a.m. Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015 Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive is the sultry Emilia Clarke Sponsored Links NEW YORK â€” 
It's most definitely Emilia Clarke's year. 
The 28-year-old Londoner, who plays menacing, white-haired Daenerys Targaryen, aka Khaleesi, aka Mother of Dragons on "Game of Thrones," is Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive. 
The magazine made the announcement early Tuesday, but GQ got there first, anointing Clarke Woman of the Year in September. 
In addition to her high-profile role on the massively popular HBO series, Clarke was Sarah Connor in the summer movie hit "Terminator: Genisys." Copyright The Associated Press Sign up for our WHIO-TV Daily Headlines Newsletter Sign Up
